    public class SolverOptionsPanel
extends javax.swing.JDialog
implements java.awt.event.FocusListener
    The solver options panel. Options such as step size and resolution are set in this panel by the user. It controls all solver types.
    Author:
    Max Comstock 2013, modified from Clinic 10-11, Aaron Becker, Martin Hunt
